{"pageContext":{"group":[{"node":{"id":"8698ca14-8c6c-5171-a871-5adcb8b83bbf","slug":"creative-and-development-inspiration-20","template":"","format":"standard","title":"Creative and Development Inspiration 20","date":"2018-03-19T13:21:08.000Z","excerpt":"<p>This week creative and development rundown is more development orientated. I have found some great packages to help enhance the user experience, as well as some alternatives to already well used solutions. Although a shorter list than usual, these items are far more usable, both in terms of using within a project and for learning more! [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.8444444444444446,"src":"/static/2d629eb7c60ebb8f4f5bd3c742c0cfe0/b4a15/m6.png","srcSet":"/static/2d629eb7c60ebb8f4f5bd3c742c0cfe0/6b34e/m6.png 250w,\n/static/2d629eb7c60ebb8f4f5bd3c742c0cfe0/9bc87/m6.png 500w,\n/static/2d629eb7c60ebb8f4f5bd3c742c0cfe0/b4a15/m6.png 913w","sizes":"(max-width: 913px) 100vw, 913px"}}}},"categories":[{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"General Coding"},{"name":"Inspiration"},{"name":"UX"}],"tags":[{"name":"Animated"},{"name":"Animation"},{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"CSS"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"Forms"},{"name":"Inspiration"},{"name":"interface"},{"name":"Interfaces"},{"name":"JS"},{"name":"microinteractions"},{"name":"Snippets"},{"name":"SVG"},{"name":"Teaching"},{"name":"Training"},{"name":"Trends"},{"name":"UX"}]}},{"node":{"id":"099ae931-5fbf-5690-8148-c679b17b745c","slug":"hit-2016-running-a-4-point-plan-to-get-you-started","template":"","format":"standard","title":"Hit 2016 Running – A 4 Point Plan To Get You Started","date":"2016-01-09T13:40:46.000Z","excerpt":"<p>Christmas and the New Year have come and gone and tens of millions of people around the world have made resolutions for the next 12 months. New Years goals about getting into shape are the most common, probably brought on by the binge drinking and food comas. Unfortuna